THE Chairman of the Peoples Democratic Party in Zamfara State, Alhaji Ibrahim Mallaha Gusau, is dead. Mallaha, a former state Chairman of the All Nigeria Peoples Party, became the Chairman of Zamfara PDP in a 2009 consensus arrangement. The leadership tussle in the state chapter of the main opposition party was resolved after his emergence. The cause of his death had not been made public as of the time of filing this report. Details laterâ€¦ 